2.1	Sales & Receivables Setup

You use the Sales & Receivables Setup to set up certain basic rules to be used in the Sales & Receivables application area.  

A number series must be setup for the records, regardless of whether the number will be manually entered into Dynamics NAV or transferred via the internface transferred via the interface.

To access the Sales & Receivables Setup, go to the following menu:
Departments/Financial Management/Receivables/Setup/Sales & Receivables Setup


